---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="LSCSS Principles"
    description="Core principles behind Layered Semantic CSS."
>
    <main class="page-shell">
        <section class="site-hero">
            <p class="eyebrow">Principles</p>

            <h1>
                Core principles
            </h1>

            <p class="intro">
                LSCSS focuses on maintainability, predictable overrides,
                readability, and scalable CSS architecture.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="content-block">
            <ul>
                <li>organise CSS in explicit layers</li>
                <li>keep styles in partials</li>
                <li>use semantic component names</li>
                <li>prefer shallow selectors</li>
                <li>keep specificity low and predictable</li>
                <li>use explicit modifier classes</li>
                <li>use visible state classes</li>
                <li>separate layout from components</li>
                <li>contain hacks and legacy code</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
